data.description: This charming residence offers a spacious and comfortable layout, ensuring you have all the space you need. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting living room that sets the perfect tone for relaxation and entertainment. The adjacent dining room is the ideal spot for hosting family and friends. The first floor boasts two generously-sized bedrooms and a well-appointed bathroom. Additionally, there's an extra den that can serve as a home office or playroom. Upstairs, you'll discover a magnificent master bedroom, complete with a luxurious bathroom that is truly a retreat of its own. The master bathroom features dual sinks, a deep soaking tub, and a remarkable 7' walk-in shower for a spa-like experience in the comfort of your own home. Spacious backyard, providing ample room for outdoor activities and a convenient location just minutes away from military bases, Norfolk Airport, shopping centers and the beautiful Norfolk beaches. Welcome Home!!
